### 6) Rounding rule CEIL_1KG
POST {{ProiectTSS_HostAddress}}/shipping/quote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone": "Local",
  "subtotal": 90,
  "options": { "rapid": false, "fragil": false },
  "parcels": [
    { "weightKg": 1.2, "size": "Small" }
  ],
  "pricingModel": "BasePlusPerKg",
  "roundingRule": "Ceil1Kg"
}

