Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone": "National",
  "subtotal": 130,
  "options": { "rapid": true, "fragil": true },
  "parcels": [
    { "weightKg": 2.5, "size": "Medium" }
  ],
  "pricingModel": "Brackets",
  "roundingRule": "None"
}

### 9) Multiple parcels list
POST {{ProiectTSS_HostAddress}}/shipping/quote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone": "International",
  "subtotal": 180,
  "options": { "rapid": false, "fragil": false },
