### 10) Coupon Percent applied on shipping
POST {{ProiectTSS_HostAddress}}/shipping/quote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone": "Local",
  "subtotal": 140,
  "options": { "rapid": false, "fragil": false },
  "parcels": [
    { "weightKg": 3.0, "size": "Medium" }
  ],
