### 14) Fallback estimator - unknown zone (null) + fallback price
POST {{ProiectTSS_HostAddress}}/shipping/quote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone": null,
  "subtotal": 100,
  "options": { "rapid": false, "fragil": false },
  "parcels": [
    { "weightKg": 1.0, "size": "Small" }
  ],
  "fallbackZonePrice": 19.5,
  "pricingModel": "Brackets",
  "roundingRule": "None"
}

